KeysToEntries.story_1_1_001:
Soon enough we,
Emperor,
will take it over…
KeysToEntries.story_1_1_002:
Never forget…
this area holds…
the White Comet.
KeysToEntries.story_1_1_003:
There’s no way
this ends smooth.
KeysToEntries.story_1_1_004:
If Kyoichi’s being
that cautious,
then I’ll head to Akagi first…
KeysToEntries.story_1_1_005:
I’ll scout
the White Comet’s home turf
real carefully…
